### ========================================
### EXERCISES - CRUD Completo
### ========================================
### Rotas protegidas (requerem token JWT)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = seu-token-aqui

### Listar todos os exercícios
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Criar novo exercício
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Supino Reto",
    "muscle_group": "Peito"
}

###

### Criar outro exercício
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Leg Press",
    "muscle_group": "Perna"
}

###

### Criar exercício sem muscle_group (opcional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Abdominal"
}

###

### Buscar exercício por ID (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar exercício (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Supino Inclinado",
    "muscle_group": "Peito"
}

###

### Deletar exercício (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

